# Market Data Provider
# Leave blank to use realistic demo data with fallback capability
# When enabled, live data will be used with automatic fallback to sample data on errors
# Options: polygon | alpaca | tradovate | binance | yahoo

# TO ENABLE LIVE DATA FOR STOCKS:
# 1. Get free API key from https://polygon.io/dashboard/api-keys
# 2. Uncomment the lines below and paste your key
# 3. Restart dev server

# VITE_MARKET_PROVIDER=polygon
# VITE_POLYGON_API_KEY=your-api-key-here

# Current: Using realistic sample data with automatic provider support
VITE_MARKET_PROVIDER=
